title: Paul Aguilar's extra-time goal puts Mexico past US 3-2 (Yahoo Sports)
text: Posts: 54,191 Paul Aguilar's extra-time goal puts Mexico past US 3-2 (Yahoo Sports) Aguilar rocketed his shot past Brad Guzan after Raul Jimenez passed the ball over his head and into the penalty area, putting a thrilling finish on the latest chapter of this rivalry at the sold-out Rose Bowl. Oribe Peralta scored a tiebreaking goal in the sixth minute of extra time for Mexico. Bobby Wood evened it in the 18th minute of extra time for the Americans, who lost to Mexico for the first time in seven games under coach Jurgen Klinsmann.
